RakeTm
======

Simple time management taks for railway workers.

Example
=======

$ rails another_startup && cd another_startup
$ script/plugin install git://github.com/antono/rake-tm.git
$ rake tm:start
...
$ autotest
$ vi test/unit/mytest.rb
...
$ rake tm:stop
$ rake tm:total

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
another_startup
Total time spent: 10:2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
personal_blog
Total time spent: 12:32

$ cat ~/.tm.log

$ rake -T tm:
rake tm:start  # Report start working on project
rake tm:stop   # Report finish working on project
rake tm:total  # Time report


